### Data sources used in demo workspaces

**OpenStreetMap** — https://www.openstreetmap.org/
License: Open Data Commons Open Database License (ODbL) v1.0
© OpenStreetMap contributors
Any map tiles or geodata derived from OpenStreetMap must carry the attribution
"© OpenStreetMap contributors" and comply with the ODbL.

**Overpass API** — https://overpass-api.de/
License: LGPL-3.0
Data from OpenStreetMap, licensed under ODbL.

Map tiles shown by default use OpenStreetMap raster tiles.
Tile URL is configurable via the `MAP_TILE_URL` environment variable to allow
self-hosted or alternative tile providers.

